//www.youtube.com/watch?v=N69fO7soqQ0&amp;feature=youtu.be\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=N69fO7soqQ0&amp;feature=youtu.be</a></li>\r\n    </ul>\r\n  </div>\r\n  <p align=\"left\">Click here to see an example of a ROS enabled autonomous, 3D mapping RMP, integrated by Stanley Innovation</p>\r\n  <div align=\"left\">\r\n    <ul>\r\n      <li><a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=au2xgDNRGV4&amp;feature=youtu.be\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=au2xgDNRGV4&amp;feature=youtu.be</a> </li>\r\n    </ul>\r\n  </div>\r\n  <p align=\"left\">Contact Stanley Innovation by email or phone:</p>\r\n  <div align=\"left\">\r\n    <ul>\r\n      <li>603-318-2716\r\n      <li><a href=\"mailto:ROS@stanleyinnovation.com\">ROS@stanleyinnovation.com</a>\r\n    </ul>\r\n  </div>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"asset-footer\"></div>\r\nIf you\'d like us to spotlight your project here, send us a note at info AT osrfoundation DOT org.\r\n<a href=\"http://www.ros.org/news/spotlight/\" target=\"_blank\">Previous spotlights</a>\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n</div>','ROS Spotlight','','inherit','closed','closed','','268-revision-v1','','','2016-03-07 21:29:54','2016-03-07 21:29:54','',268,'http://www.ros.org/268-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0);
INSERT INTO `wp_posts` VALUES (1176,1,'2016-04-18 18:34:07','2016-04-18 18:34:07','<h1 id=\"page-title\" class=\"asset-name entry-title\">ROS Spotlight: Kinetic Kame Tshirt Available</h1>\r\n<div class=\"asset-content entry-content\">\r\n<div class=\"asset-body\">\r\n\r\n\r\n<span style=\"color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12.8px;\">With each release of ROS we have a tradition of having a logo and making t-shirts. <a href=\"http://wiki.ros.org/kinetic\">ROS Kinetic Kame</a></span><span style=\"color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12.8px;\">&nbsp;is coming out in May. Show your ROS colors and support this tradition!&nbsp; Visit the&nbsp;</span><a href=\"http://bit.ly/KinteicKame\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"color: rgb(17, 85, 204); font-family: arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12.8px;\">Teespring Campaign page here</a><span style=\"color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12.8px;\">&nbsp;to order your shirt.&nbsp;</span><br style=\"color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12.8px;\" /><br style=\"color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12.8px;\" /><a href=\"http://www.ros.org/news/2016/04/18/kinetic_tshirt_front.png\"><img alt=\"kinetic_tshirt_front.png\" src=\"http://www.ros.org/news/assets_c/2016/04/kinetic_tshirt_front-thumb-640x761-1431.png\" width=\"640\" height=\"761\" class=\"mt-image-center\" style=\"text-align: center; display: block; margin: 0 auto 20px;\" /></a><br style=\"color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12.8px;\" /><span style=\"color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12.8px;\">Proceeds from shirt sales go to supporting the costs associated with developing and maintaining ROS, including hosting the wiki and running the build farm.&nbsp;</span><br style=\"color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12.8px;\" /><br style=\"color: rgb(34, 34